name: chapter III : 𝖑𝖔𝖘𝖙
description:
abandoned bodies, angels playing and people waiting, a complete calm everywhere, a calm that makes you feel insecure everywhere.
no one calls each other by name, unidentified people waiting for their identification, souls who ask for their names, beings who do not know what happened, their faces / memories cloudy, hiding their cries, feeling like a sunday. The wait is eternal .... and I think I am on the 21st of 49 to return.
